---
title: Fattoush-Inspired Falafel Salad with Spiced Flatbreads and Feta Cheese
description: Everything about this salad delights! Our take on this Mediterranean dish is layered with roasted garlic dressing, fresh herbs and veggies, crispy chickpeas, protein-rich falafel and flavourful, crunchy flatbread.
